---
title: Nan's Roast Pumpkin & Haloumi Toss with Flaked Almonds & Creamy Pesto Dressing
description: Tossing everything together is a lot of fun and allows for all the flavours to melt into each other. For example, this roasted
pumpkin sprinkled in Nan’s special seasoning combines with herby veggies to form the ultimate combo. The salt of cooked
haloumi balances out the veggies perfectly. An easy win for a weeknight dinner.

